{"tid":2106554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司法機構收大量投訴涉同一法官　今起網上刊回應 ","createTime":"2020-07-13T11:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T11:52:16.000Z","uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb6c1f6c2dd1fb40e01ed48ee8536d77bbbedf0","tid":2106554,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>司法機構收大量投訴涉同一法官　今起網上刊回應 </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n司法機構今日（13日）表示，最近一直收到大量涉及同一名法官或司法人員、性質相同或類似的投訴，該些投訴關乎若干司法決定和法庭案件。根據終審法院首席法官的指示，為更有效傳達信息及處理該等投訴，由今日起，投訴法官行為秘書處可在適當情況下，按照相關法院領導的指示，把該等投訴的要點及有關的回應上載至司法機構網頁，以代替就每宗投訴作個別回覆。<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n另外，為免影響司法獨立，若投訴涉及尚在進行的法庭程序（包括上訴），司法機構會待所有相關法庭程序完結後，才會處理有關投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200713/s00001/1594625844942/司法機構收大量投訴涉同一法官-今起網上刊回應\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200713%2Fs00001%2F1594625844942%2F%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E6%94%B6%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E6%B6%89%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98-%E4%BB%8A%E8%B5%B7%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%88%8A%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=07f6758e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200713%2Fs00001%2F1594625844942%2F%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E6%94%B6%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E6%B6%89%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98-%E4%BB%8A%E8%B5%B7%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%88%8A%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89&h=e9e5c8d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200713/s00001/1594625844942/司法機構收大量投訴涉同一法官-今起網上刊回應</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.judiciary.hk/zh/about_us/similar_complaints.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.hk%2Fzh%2Fabout_us%2Fsimilar_complaints.html&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=78ca32ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ju